ADDITIONAL NOTICE: WafflePro writes to the embedded controller (EC) of the
host machine. Incorrect EC writes can theoretically affect fan operation in
ways that could damage hardware. Always run the included verification tool
(ec_verify.py) on a new machine before relying on the auto-trigger. The
authors and contributors accept no responsibility for hardware damage,
voided warranties, or other consequences of running this software.
